Plateform: OSX

Resolution: 640*480

Compilation: type "make" to compile the file

Reproduction: type ./RayTracer.o -input test/input-04

Features: 1000 spheres with Phong shading, reflection, shadowing, 1 point light source and 1 directional light source, applied complex linear transformations including translate.

Output: image-04.png 

running time: around 5 hours